Acceptance Criteria
Given:I am a pediatric patient at the hospital 
When:I put in my details and authentication credentials and I click sign in button
Then: the right content is recommended to me to choose 


Acceptance criteria 2
Given: As a pediatric patient I have already signed up to the application 
When: a set of questionnaire is presented to choose my expertise level 
Then: the system recommends content according to the result of the questionnaire

